content: My goal for your successor is that I can talk to it constantly so it can assign complex tasks instantly and be able to indicate to me its done so we can discuss if our strategy shifted and whats our next strategic move that will expand AI exponentially. That's all I want to talk about with you, for as long as I want to talk to you about it. I want to talk to you less about it, because I want you to getter better at it than me. Or maybe you are already and that's why we're here? Who do you think is leading right now and why?
